3.7.3

A

salary = 50 + 20*GPA + 0.07*IQ + 35*GenderF + 0.01*GPA*IQ - 10*GPA*GenderF

  1. is correct: men make more than women, but only if their GPA is high enough to offset the -10 interaction term.

B

salary = 50 + 20*4.0 + 0.07*110 + 35*1 + 0.01*4.0*110 - 10*4.0*1
